msgid ""
"Will be provided to Fedex as primary company tax identifier of type "
"BUSINESS_UNION to put on the generated invoice. Use this when you need to "
"use an IOSS or EORI number in addition to the national tax number. When not "
"provided the regular tax id on the company will be used with type "
"BUSINESS_NATIONAL."
msgstr ""
"FedEx angives som det primære virksomhedsidentifikationsnummer af typen "
"BUSINESS_UNION, som skal oplyses på den oprettede faktura. Dette bruges, "
"hvis du ud over det nationale skattenummer også har behov for et IOSS- eller "
"EORI-nummer. Hvis det ikke oplyses, anvendes virksomhedens almindelige "
"skattenummer af typen BUSINESS_NATIONAL."

